Title: Nothing Important Happened Today (1)
Plot: Agent Doggett investigates the death of an EPA official after his car is forced off a bridge by a woman he picked up. He asks for assistance on the case from Scully, who has returned to her teaching position at the FBI Academy in Quantico.
GuestStars: Lucy Lawless, Nicholas Walker, John Casino, Jane Yamamoto, Ashley Knutson, Rikki Held, Rowdy Held
